AMPIRE CO LTD August Sales Fall 3.60% (Table) : 8049 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-09-09T07:31:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/ampire-co-ltd-august-sales-fall-3-60-table-8049-tt.html
AMPIRE CO LTD (8049)  said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 3.60% to NT$129,594,000 from NT$134,435,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales            129,594          134,435    
YOY%              -3.60%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            915,967         1,049,452   
YOY%             -12.72% 
=================================================================
 